{"tid":2345091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大交合話強烈寒潮就快襲港 準備好幫我收屍...","createTime":"2020-12-29T08:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T10:26:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3c3ed773064ecdfd4445d133b36e3c70f51822","tid":2345091,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"一道冷鋒正橫過廣東北部，該區氣溫普遍較昨日下降10度左右。預料該冷鋒會在晚間抵達廣東沿岸，與其相關的強烈寒潮隨後會逐漸影響本港。<br />\n<br />\n本港地區今晚及明日天氣預測<br />\n<br />\n天氣顯著轉冷。明早部分時間多雲，最低氣溫約12度。日間漸轉天晴乾燥，氣溫上升至15度左右。明晚市區氣溫進一步降至約10度，新界再低兩三度。吹微風，晚間北風增強，離岸及高地吹烈風。<br />\n<br />\n展望 : 除夕及元旦市區早上氣溫更降至7、8度，新界再低兩三度，天晴及非常乾燥。週末期間早上氣溫仍然偏低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(以上預測有效期至明日(2020年12月30日)23時59分;<br />\n定期更新時間：約每小時45分，16時15分及23時15分)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f93675d941a9a5d07acfcd9579d3cbbf1657397","tid":2345091,"uid":86596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"幫你照顧彩瑛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bc7f87e853628201614951768ad243389a22c1","tid":2345091,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90996d1103d79eebcd558e494c90e79282ea583","tid":2345091,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:50:15.000Z","msg":"我會攬住彩瑛同Mina 瞓 <br />\n你去死啦"},{"pid":"461049fb6e5160e2ee7eb6730db27b8a88045c31","tid":2345091,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"食肥自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance